   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession">
            <pb n="1r"/>
                <opener>
                    <address>
                  <addrLine>
                            <choice>
                        <abbr>Sr</abbr>
                        <expan>Seiner</expan>
                     </choice> Wohlgeboren</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>dem Herrn <choice>
                        <abbr>D.</abbr>
                        <expan>Doktor</expan>
                     </choice> Ehrenberg</addrLine>
               </address>
            </opener>
            <pb n="1v"/>
                <p>Herzlichen Dank, mein Verehrtester <lb/>für Ihre wichtige <ref xml:id="ac578e6f-8ab1-466e-978e-6f8ab1c66ecd" corresp="#d79161b7-5e26-4111-9161-b75e2641118c">Abhandlung <lb/>über die <choice>
                        <abbr>geogr.</abbr>
                        <expan>geographische</expan>
                     </choice> Vertheilung <lb/>der Scorpione</ref>
                    <note xml:id="d79161b7-5e26-4111-9161-b75e2641118c" corresp="#ac578e6f-8ab1-466e-978e-6f8ab1c66ecd">
                     <bibl corresp="https://edition-humboldt.de/v8/ECEMJELH">Ehrenberg 1829c</bibl>
                  </note>. Hat denn <lb/>
                    <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/11669811X">Rüppel</persName>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>od.</abbr>
                  <expan>oder</expan>
               </choice>
               <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/102458561">Cordier</persName> nicht <lb/>den <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/349401">Sinai</placeName> barometrisch <lb/>gemessen.</p>
            <p>Aus den besten Arbeiten <lb/>folgt <lb/>
                    <list>
                  <item>1° cent = ~~ Tropen aus meiner eigenen</item>
                  <item>187 mètres ~~ <choice>
                        <abbr>Beob.</abbr>
                        <expan>Beobachtung</expan>
                     </choice> 1° <choice>
                        <abbr>R</abbr>
                        <expan>Réaumur</expan>
                     </choice>= 700 Fuß</item>
               </list>
               <milestone unit="section" rendition="#hr"/>
               <lb/>~~ temperirte Zone auch <lb/>
               <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118804790">Saussure</persName>, <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/118787802">Ramond</persName>, <persName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/117668729">D’ <lb/> Aubuisson</persName>
               <table rows="3" cols="2">
                  <row>
                     <cell>1° <choice>
                           <abbr>C</abbr>
                           <expan>Celsius</expan>
                        </choice> =172<hi rendition="#sup">m</hi>
                        <lb/>en été</cell>
                     <cell>1° <choice>
                           <abbr>R</abbr>
                           <expan>Réaumur</expan>
                        </choice> = 520 <del rendition="#s">
                                    <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="words"/>
                                </del>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Par</abbr>
                           <expan>Pariser</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <lb/>Fuß im Sommer</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>1° <choice>
                           <abbr>C.</abbr>
                           <expan>Celsius</expan>
                        </choice> = 230<hi rendition="#sup">m</hi>
                        <lb/>en hiver</cell>
                     <cell>aber 707 Fuß <lb/>im Winter</cell>
                  </row>
               </table>Ich rathe Ihnen 1° <choice>
                  <abbr>R.</abbr>
                  <expan>Réaumur</expan>
               </choice>
               <lb/>= 600 <choice>
                  <abbr>F.</abbr>
                  <expan>Fuß</expan>
               </choice> zu nehmen</p>
            <closer rend="paragraph">
                    <signed>Ihr <lb/>AHumboldt</signed>
               <dateline>Donnerstags</dateline>
                </closer>
         </div>
